{"tid":1962412,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"真愛是否命中注定","createTime":"2020-04-07T12:43:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-09T05:19:34.000Z","uid":249885,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a14147a9ea2f816e21cab243f4963ebdc4986167","tid":1962412,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T12:43:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/HQkB1OmDLhI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FHQkB1OmDLhI&d=BHyrWEjohbhGCquuSPOYYgpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=a7cc33ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/HQkB1OmDLhI</a><br />\n簡單嚟講就係：客觀嚟講 唔會有個&quot;神&quot;去安排你同邊個相遇 所以如果因為相信呢句說話而唔提升自己 係不可取嘅<br />\n<br />\n但如果你見到嗰個人，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">覺得</span>同佢嘅相遇係命中注定，咁個就係你嘅真愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n即係命中註定唔存在，但你信就係真愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf207b255d9d3562094a8c136f8d2c3a1bdab757","tid":1962412,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T12:48:09.000Z","msg":"推下先"},{"pid":"9cf3b5ffe480e4da9cae8432b461b0fb54bb5d85","tid":1962412,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T12:50:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f40d4fa3058faa82ad8eb30b30c58192ac814ed1","tid":1962412,"uid":134103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T12:51:07.000Z","msg":"講得幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#lik"},{"pid":"55683d8af00487390c56125b9d67d38165cea937","tid":1962412,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f40d4fa3058faa82ad8eb30b30c58192ac814ed1","tid":1962412,"uid":134103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T12:51:07.000Z","msg":"講得幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#lik"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T12:52:22.000Z","msg":"thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f296d0eb40a39d845b50c36df03f0f07dc81c86","tid":1962412,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T12:54:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fb281a27b5f1d7cb3109ff2639e0cfff4717b9e2","tid":1962412,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T12:58:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1298bc878256290a04e93ee5706ea6b96d59bbba","tid":1962412,"uid":886,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T13:00:14.000Z","msg":"500 Days of Summer：<br />\n如果你不曾感到對方是命中注定，你未曾嘗過戀愛<br />\n<br />\nBy好青年荼毒室<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://corrupttheyouth.net/2017/02/13/500-days-of-summer%EF%BC%9A%E5%A6%82%E6%9E%9C%E4%BD%A0%E4%B8%8D%E6%9B%BE%E6%84%9F%E5%88%B0%E5%B0%8D%E6%96%B9%E6%98%AF%E5%91%BD%E4%B8%AD%E6%B3%A8%E5%AE%9A%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%A0%E6%9C%AA%E6%9B%BE%E5%98%97/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcorrupttheyouth.net%2F2017%2F02%2F13%2F500-days-of-summer%25EF%25BC%259A%25E5%25A6%2582%25E6%259E%259C%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%259B%25BE%25E6%2584%259F%25E5%2588%25B0%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%2591%25BD%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%25B3%25A8%25E5%25AE%259A%25EF%25BC%258C%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E6%259C%25AA%25E6%259B%25BE%25E5%2598%2597%2F&d=BHyrWEjohbhGCquuSPOYYgpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=251a88a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://corrupttheyouth.net/2017/02/13/500-days-of-summer%EF%BC%9A%E5%A6%82%E6%9E%9C%E4%BD%A0%E4%B8%8D%E6%9B%BE%E6%84%9F%E5%88%B0%E5%B0%8D%E6%96%B9%E6%98%AF%E5%91%BD%E4%B8%AD%E6%B3%A8%E5%AE%9A%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%A0%E6%9C%AA%E6%9B%BE%E5%98%97/</a><br />\n<br />\n//「羅漫蒂克命定論」在認知上無疑是虛幻的，卻不代表它荒誕無謂。事實上，在「命中注定」的宣稱背後，潛藏着我們內心深處的焦慮：<span style=\"color: red;\">我們害怕跟愛人分開，害怕世界沒有秩序，於是陳構一個說法，保證自己的戀情。若說愛情是命中注定，就好像事物有了秩序，關係有了保障，我們的感覺會踏實一點。</span><br />\n<br />\n　　反而，若然相信所有人的相遇都是巧合，那麼錯失一班航機，錯失一次食店偶遇，軌跡改變，角度交錯，則我這輩子的摯愛、現在每日與我分擔悲與喜的另一半，也許只是街上面目模糊的陌路人。但是我根本不願意相信，現在我的摯愛就像是街上隨手攔截的計程車、酒店隨時替換的毛巾，只是湊巧碰上。<span style=\"color: red;\">一旦我真心相信所有事情的發生純屬巧合，就意味着我同時承認，所謂「摯愛」在我的生命其實是一場意外，可有可無。換言之，一旦我這樣想，我已經沒有那樣愛她。</span>"},{"pid":"2a187c90d598202881b592e7a21e37bf1a19ab9f","tid":1962412,"uid":1779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T13:01:04.000Z","msg":"聽佢講野好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f207fb0a5874d6e3b0419283b4ed0f775e61bc6","tid":1962412,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T13:07:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"22fed7f2db76415cb2b8b612337b24405b245bf2","tid":1962412,"uid":257773,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T13:27:41.000Z","msg":"神會安排你去遇見 然後安排他離開<br />\n遇見不難 比重逢容易"},{"pid":"ef74a70090a578bad0e771a4eb75744acd2dcb96","tid":1962412,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T13:54:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b4e159524c9e03520c4527f097e7218c7aede3fb","tid":1962412,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T14:08:04.000Z","msg":"無"},{"pid":"953d3d0679575cf1e523c42729f84bd640223545","tid":1962412,"uid":39215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T14:09:13.000Z","msg":"其實根本冇愛呢樣野<br />\n一齊都係一場交易"},{"pid":"4285702dccfde56c05dd5dc8ed202a0999f465b1","tid":1962412,"uid":310871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T14:18:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5f6ec0d71ac7a3ce36d81ee4324a5cd10fb28248","tid":1962412,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T14:34:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1c83a81e3f3bb5fd412e573f2a61c6d1c75f8628","tid":1962412,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4e159524c9e03520c4527f097e7218c7aede3fb","tid":1962412,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T14:08:04.000Z","msg":"無"},"cite